    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/Flyers_Clips/status/2037344882398826862",
      "reply_text": "Yeah, they can turn it on like that. But it's all about sustaining it.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-27T01:53:51.193805+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/nick__xo/status/2037339388405858477",
      "reply_text": "Kevin Huerter's value is definitely on the rise",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-27T01:54:28.853520+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/KeithSmithNBA/status/2037340857062305910",
      "reply_text": "High-end backup is a great floor for Smith. Agree on the loaded draft class.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-27T01:55:01.789929+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/APH00PS/status/2037322909140619524",
      "reply_text": "Kawhi's numbers are great, but what about his age and injury history? That's a different story.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-27T01:55:56.803775+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/CREAMYCOLE/status/2037334106841772191",
      "reply_text": "I'd still rep the Grizzlies. They're my hometown team.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-27T01:56:37.058264+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/MavsFilmRoom/status/2037337204947869971",
      "reply_text": "Lottery is still a ways off, but these matchups are already giving me some thoughts on their potential NBA careers.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-27T01:57:08.378421+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/roddystr/status/2037342338649883008",
      "reply_text": "Impressive all-around game. 82ts% is elite for a rookie.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-27T01:57:43.744606+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/NBABlackburn/status/2037312469077766227",
      "reply_text": "That's a lot of dimes. He's really pushing the pace.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-27T01:58:18.740520+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/APH00PS/status/2037339375990649079",
      "reply_text": "That's a stretch. Those teams don't have the cap space",
