    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/Dame_Lillard/status/2037305760779284669",
      "reply_text": "Coach Raym is a great motivator. Players love him.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-27T01:59:41.624054+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/LegionHoops/status/2037306108071571545",
      "reply_text": "Yeah Russ was coming off the bench that season. Still a weird move",
